### expected behaviour
pictures from folders shared with me shall appear in the picture application.

### actual behaviour
pictures in folders that were shared with my account do not appear in the gallery application.

this is a regression from older releases in 4.x branch

### steps to reproduce
1. user a shares a picture folder with user b
2. user b see the folder in his "shared" folder
3. user b do not see the folder in the gallery application

### server configuration
operating system: debian squeeze

web server: apache 2.2.16

database: mysql 5.1

php version: 5.3.3

owncloud version: 5.0.6

### client configuration
browser: firefox 21

operating system: ubuntu 13.04

